OL,3,CStoneham beat Cockfosters on penalties
OL,4,Cto lift FA vase
OL,6,FAFC Stoneham have capped off the
OL,7,Fperfect season by winning the FA Vase
OL,8,Fat Wembley.
OL,10,FThe Hampshire club won a penalty shoot-
OL,11,Fout 4-2 against Cockfosters FC after a
OL,12,Fgoalless 90 minutes.
OL,14,FBoth sides hit the crossbar during the
OL,15,Fgame, but the Purps scored all their
OL,16,Fpenalty kicks while the Fosters missed
OL,17,Ftwo.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
