OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779127867
OL,3,CStoneham beat Cockfosters on penalties
OL,4,Cto lift FA vase
OL,6,FCallum Laycock and Jake Thomson scored
OL,7,FStoneham's first two while
OL,8,FCockfosters' George Lutaaya also found
OL,9,Fthe net.
OL,11,FAdam Hastings then stepped up but his
OL,12,Feffort was saved by Stoneham keeper
OL,13,FCallum Lee.
OL,15,FTom Annetts, Max Jessop and Tyrrell
OL,16,FSampson then followed with perfect
OL,17,Fspot-kicks before Junior Moses sent
OL,18,Fhis high over the bar, handing
OL,19,FStoneham the vase.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
